    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing around 25 species of medium- to large-sized trees native to tropical regions of Central and South America. Valued for hard wood that becomes dark purplish brown upon exposure to UV light.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
